properties.LOCATION_DESCR: The province is made up of many boundaries which were capatured from various sources.  The international boundary is very accurate (1m) while the Hudson Bay boundary is from the NTS 1:250,000 and is not very accurate. •	Ottawa River to St. Lawrence River – resurveyed jointly by Ontario & Quebec in 2011. Finalized April 8, 2015. Coordinates are MTM zone 8 NAD 83 CSRS Accuracy of <1m See CL 16503
